tab1.text1:
Welcome too the DoDo Chaos Ascended 100X PvE Server

We hope you enjoy your stay!

For complaints or reporting an issue please make a ticket in the discord or report an issue ingame...

- F1 too report an issue

- F2 for leaving a review of the server

- F3 for voting on our server this will be much appreciated

- F4 for getting back in this menu.


Our server works with discord and a community webpage with a integrated shop
Too join Discord click on the Discord button below
Too join the community website click on the website button below

Wanna stay updated about the server join our discord or community webpage so you don't get left out
Interact with other player enter Give-Aways and stay updated about upcoming Events

We hope too see you there

Have fun!

tab2.text2:
1: No Spamming structures in the map.

2: Making a dino trap no problem after taming please demolish it!

3: Don't Spam or leave your dino's in somebody else his base

4: No MASS breeding this will kill the server

5: If not online please cryo as much of your dinos as you can

6: Admins are not responable if you lose anything

7: Structures and Dino's have a decay timer on them

8: No insiding allowed

9: Keep it fair and lovely people!
